"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/49133","Department for Communities and Local Government","false","2014-05-07","<p> </p><p>The Department does not collect detailed information on the staff roles employed by local authorities.</p><p> </p>","Great Yarmouth","Brandon Lewis",,"2014-05-07T12:00:00.00Z","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/49133/answer","Biography information for Brandon Lewis","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/49133/answer",,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/49133/answer",,,,,"7","Communities and Local Government","Communities and Local Government","2014-04-29",,"1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Communities and Local Government, how many environmental health officers are currently employed by each local authority.","false","Biography information for Tim Farron","Westmorland and Lonsdale","Tim Farron","197200"
